%F A397819 Equals (n/L(n)) * sqrt(1/2 + sqrt(5)*F(n)/4) * sqrt(1/2 + sqrt(1/2 + sqrt(5)*F(n)/4)/2) * sqrt(1/2 + sqrt(1/2 + sqrt(1/2 + sqrt(5)*F(n)/4)/2)/2) * ... for n odd, where F(n) = A000045(n) and L(n) = A000032(n) (Osler, 2007).
%F A397819 Equals 1/(2*A002390) = 1/A202543 = A160509/2.
%F A397819 Equals A397818 / A002163.
